e_Cnihelthus = {
	color = { 0 0 0 }
	color2 = { 255 255 255 }
	capital = c_Cebrhelum

	can_create = {
			NOT = {
			faith = {
				religion_tag = christianity_religion
				has_doctrine = doctrine_spiritual_head
			}
		}
	}

	ai_primary_priority = {
		if = {
			limit = {
				culture_group = culture_group:central_germanic_group
			}
			add = @correct_culture_primary_score
		}
	}

			NOT = {
			faith = {
				religion_tag = christianity_religion
				has_doctrine = doctrine_spiritual_head
			}
		}
	}

	ai_primary_priority = {
		if = {
			limit = {
				culture_group = culture_group:central_germanic_group
			}
			add = @correct_culture_primary_score
		}
	}

			NOT = {
			faith = {

e_Mantingorgdos = {
	color = { 46 104 39 }
	color2 = { 255 255 255 }

	can_create = {
			NOT = {
			faith = {
				religion_tag = christianity_religion
				has_doctrine = doctrine_spiritual_head
			}
		}
	}

	ai_primary_priority = {
		if = {
			limit = {
				culture_group = culture_group:central_germanic_group
			}
			add = @correct_culture_primary_score
		}
	}

		}
